sidering non-necrotizing granulomas without evidence of TB or fungi.","dimension":12,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.0322,0.05597,0.072402,0.081597,0.091307,0.095705,0.099397,0.099697,0.097978,0.096495,0.09105,0.086202],"unified_progress":[0.036516,0.063731,0.077472,0.087155,0.092391,0.095825,0.095776,0.096151,0.095455,0.092304,0.086537,0.080687]},{"section":18,"text":"What else causes granulomas?","dimension":6,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.03326,0.053557,0.070472,0.080522,0.09125,0.096744,0.10046,0.10262,0.10025,0.10174,0.089729,0.079405],"unified_progress":[0.03502,0.062374,0.078065,0.089563,0.094448,0.098753,0.099798,0.098875,0.09648,0.096916,0.083098,0.066609]},{"section":19,"text":"Well, there's sarcoidosis.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027913,0.051563,0.069529,0.081231,0.093769,0.1004,0.10763,0.10959,0.10443,0.10107,0.084052,0.068824],"unified_progress":[0.031339,0.060734,0.080978,0.094474,0.10014,0.10814,0.10549,0.10222,0.096721,0.092325,0.07321,0.054227]},{"section":20,"text":"Sarcoidosis is characterized by non-caseating granulomas and often involves the lungs and lymph nodes.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.024767,0.047313,0.063811,0.077887,0.093693,0.10231,0.1158,0.11827,0.10997,0.097701,0.081962,0.066508],"unified_progress":[0.027078,0.056035,0.079753,0.095899,0.1031,0.11524,0.11044,0.10583,0.09851,0.089639,0.068047,0.05044]},{"section":21,"text":"It can present with symptoms like shortness of breath, fatigue, and chest pain.","dimension":14,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.041574,0.083012,0.077516,0.071719,0.079117,0.081205,0.0869,0.092019,0.093542,0.082209,0.10274,0.10845],"unified_progress":[0.096931,0.13052,0.10296,0.089155,0.086951,0.085382,0.079736,0.084082,0.075355,0.067397,0.057041,0.044486]},{"section":22,"text":"Another possibility is Wegener's granulomatous disease, but that usually involves other systems like the kidneys and sinuses, and the granulomas are necrotizing.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029172,0.050953,0.066338,0.077434,0.091462,0.098194,0.10816,0.11077,0.10666,0.099412,0.086153,0.075293],"unified_progress":[0.036375,0.063973,0.1065,0.098214,0.1031,0.11161,0.10255,0.094078,0.089639,0.079499,0.064022,0.050449]},{"section":23,"text":"Also, her symptoms don't point to that as much.","dimension":0,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030325,0.052091,0.067901,0.077943,0.088358,0.094443,0.10075,0.10416,0.10669,0.10478,0.095103,0.077443],"unified_progress":[0.03706,0.064278,0.079906,0.088524,0.096294,0.097541,0.097912,0.1005,0.097965,0.099353,0.080242,0.060427]},{"section":24,"text":"Could it be something like histoplasmosis?","dimension":5,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.022998,0.042088,0.059558,0.074534,0.088693,0.10111,0.11211,0.11706,0.11752,0.10813,0.090404,0.065802],"unified_progress":[0.029415,0.065712,0.085983,0.098929,0.10159,0.10312,0.10484,0.10232,0.096869,0.091083,0.072184,0.047957]},{"section":25,"text":"But that would likely have positive fungal stains.","dimension":0,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029919,0.052239,0.068468,0.07942,0.08958,0.096094,0.1037,0.10645,0.10639,0.10296,0.09084,0.073933],"unified_progress":[0.033353,0.061563,0.079057,0.090232,0.097773,0.10077,0.10214,0.10255,0.098863,0.095974,0.079412,0.058317]},{"section":26,"text":"Same with other fungal infections.","dimension":12,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033585,0.050971,0.068657,0.08002,0.09136,0.09819,0.10412,0.10649,0.10614,0.10146,0.088448,0.070551],"unified_progress":[0.037616,0.062868,0.079472,0.090659,0.097251,0.10055,0.10151,0.10104,0.098263,0.094851,0.078403,0.057518]},{"section":27,"text":"Since the stains are negative, that's less likely.","dimension":0,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.026727,0.054149,0.071511,0.08224,0.090317,0.094865,0.100